-- Disaster and environment plans and strategies are not adequately implemented due to inadequate resources and awareness;
-- No National Disaster  Management Plan in place to describe strategies and stakeholder roles on Disaster Risk Reduction Management (DRRM)
-- A weakly functioning early warning system exists in Sudan, which leads to enhanced exposure of communities to natural hazards; 
--Scattered information on disaster risks exist, but no comprehensive risk analysis available for Sudan;
